MENU TITLE OS Install Menu

LABEL Centos6-Vagrant-vbox
MENU LABEL Create Vagrant Centos 6 Base Box
kernel centos6/srv/isolinux/vmlinuz append initrd=centos6/srv/isolinux/initrd.img inst.repo=http://192.168.4.10/centos6/srv ip=dhcp ks=http://192.168.4.10/ks/vagrant.vbox.centos6

